{{Top|leg}}
The '''HD-234-C''' was a small [[Berry/Legends|berry]]-picking droid used with [[CD-2 Harvester]]s and the [[R0/5T.N1 tree feeder|5T Tree Feeder]]. It was used, and made, by the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]] and was rarely found outside of the Consortium's borders.<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref> It was designed to pick fruit and vegetables from plants and trees.

